summary.span: 所有的集合指定工作表中的对象。

span.span: A collection of all the objects on the specified worksheet.

summary.span: 每一个 OLEObject 对象都代表一个 ActiveX 控件或者一个链接或嵌入的 OLE 对象。

span.span: Each OLEObject object represents an ActiveX control or a linked or embedded OLE object.
Use the method to return the OLEObjects collection.

para.span: 使用方法可创建新的 OLE 对象并将其添加到OLEObjects集合。

span.span: Use the method to create a new OLE object and add it to the OLEObjects collection.

para.span: 工作表上的 ActiveX 控件有两个名称：一个是包含该控件的形状的名称，查看工作表时可在“名称”框中看到它；另一个是控件的代码名称，可以在“属性”窗口中“(名称)”右边的单元格中看到它。在您首次向工作表添加控件时，形状名称和代码名称是一致的。但是，如果您更改这两个名称中的任意一个，另一个不会随之自动更改。

span.span: An ActiveX control on a sheet has two names: the name of the shape that contains the control, which you can see in the Name box when you view the sheet, and the code name for the control, which you can see in the cell to the right of (Name) in the Properties window. When you first add a control to a sheet, the shape name and code name match. However, if you change either the shape name or code name, the other is not automatically changed to match.

para.span: 在名称的事件过程，您使用控件的代码名称。

span.span: You use the code name of a control in the names of its event procedures.

para.span: 但是，当您返回控件从或工作表的OLEObjects集合，您必须使用形状的名称，而不是代码名称，按名称引用的控件。

span.span: However, when you return a control from the or OLEObjects collection for a sheet, you must use the shape name, not the code name, to refer to the control by name.

para.span: 例如，假定您向工作表添加复选框和默认形状的名称和默认代码名称是 CheckBox1。

span.span: For example, assume that you add a check box to a sheet and that both the default shape name and the default code name are CheckBox1.

para.span: 如果您后来更改控件代码名称，通过在属性窗口中键入 chkFinished 旁边 （名称），您必须使用 chkFinished 在事件过程名称，但您仍需要使用 CheckBox1 从形状或OLEObjects返回控件集合。

span.span: If you then change the control code name by typing chkFinished next to (Name) in the Properties window, you must use chkFinished in event procedures names, but you still have to use CheckBox1 to return the control from the Shapes or OLEObjects collection.

MemberSignature.Value: public: property bool AutoLoad { bool get(); void set(bool value); };

summary.span: 打开，则返回 true如果包含该工作簿时自动加载的 OLE 对象。

span.span: True if the OLE object is automatically loaded when the workbook that contains it is opened.

para.span: ActiveX 忽略此属性。打开一个工作簿时总会载入 ActiveX 控件。

span.span: This property is ignored by ActiveX controls. ActiveX controls are always loaded when a workbook is opened.

para.span: 对于大多数 OLE 对象类型，此属性不能设为 True。对于新 OLE 对象，默认情况下其 AutoLoad 属性设为 False；当 Microsoft Excel 载入工作簿时，设为“False”可节省时间和内存。自动载入 OLE 对象的好处在于，对于代表易变动的数据的对象，可立即重建到数据源的链接，而且，如果需要，可对这些对象进行重新映射。

span.span: For most OLE object types, this property shouldn’t be set to True. By default, the AutoLoad property is set to False for new OLE objects; this saves time and memory when Microsoft Excel is loading workbooks. The benefit of automatically loading OLE objects is that, for objects that represent volatile data, links to source data can be reestablished immediately and the objects can be rendered again, if necessary.
